gov.nih.nci.hl7.ui.jgraph.functions
Interface FunctionBoxMutableViewInterface

All Superinterfaces:
BaseObject, java.lang.Cloneable
All Known Implementing Classes:
FunctionBoxMutableViewInterfaceImpl
public interface FunctionBoxMutableViewInterface
extends BaseObject

This interface defines a list of contracts that need to be delivered for a functional box view representation. A default implementation of this class is provided by FunctionBoxMutableViewInterfaceImpl. This interface represents a mutable instance of functional box usage.
